'''Basra''' (afka carabiga; '''البصرة)''' waa magaalo qadiimi ah oo ku taala dalka [[ciraaq]], waxaa dhisay [[Cutba bin gazwaan|Cutba bin Gazwaan]] xiligii khaliifkii [[Cumar (saxaaba)|Cumar bin khadaaab]], waxayna noqotay magaaladii ugu horaysay ee Islaami ah oo ay [[Carabta|Carabtu]] ka dhistaan meel ka baxsan Jaziirada Carabta<ref>{{استشهاد ويب|مسار=https://www.alkhaleej.ae/%D9%85%D9%84%D8%AD%D9%82/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A8%D9%80%D8%B5%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%83%D8%B2-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%88%D9%85-%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A9|عنوان=البـصرة{{Dead link|date=Bisha Tobnaad 2022 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}.. مركز العلوم والتجارة|ناشر=موقع الخليج|مسار أرشيف=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110195409/https://www.alkhaleej.ae/%D9%85%D9%84%D8%AD%D9%82/%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%A8%D9%80%D8%B5%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D9%80%D8%B1%D8%A9-%D9%85%D8%B1%D9%83%D8%B2-%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%B9%D9%84%D9%88%D9%85-%D9%88%D8%A7%D9%84%D8%AA%D8%AC%D8%A7%D8%B1%D8%A9%7C%D8%AA%D8%A7%D8%B1%D9%8A%D8%AE أرشيف=10 نوفمبر 2020</ref>, Waa mid ka mid ah [[Caasimad|magaalooyinka]] waaweyn ee [[Carabta|Carbeedeed]], kaalinta shan iyo tobnaad ayee gashay xaga tirada dadka marka loo eego tirakoobka 2007. 
== Taariikhda ==
[[Furashada ciraaq|Furashada islaamka ee ciraaq]] ka dib waxaa soo baxday baahi ah dhisida magaalooyin ay caskarta dagaan una noqoto saldhig rasmi u ah sidaas darteed ayuu khaliifka islaamka [[Cumar bin Khadaab|cumar bin khadaab]] ku amray [[cutba bin gazawaan]] inuu dhiso magaalo, [[Cutba bin gazawaan|Cutba]] ayaa ka dhisay magaalada basra isku taga wabiyada [[Tigris|dijla]] iyo [[furaat]] agtiis sanadkii 14aad hijrada ama 15aad<ref>{{استشهاد|ناشر=[[أي بي سي-كليو]]|مكان النشر=Santa Barbara, USA|editor1=Michael R.T. Dumper|editor2=Bruce E. Stanley|مؤلف=Bruce Stanley|الفصل=Basrah|عنوان=Cities of the Middle East and North Africa|تاريخ النشر2008|صفحة=72</ref>, kadib waxaa kusoo batay qabiilada carabta ee dageesa, waxaa laga dhisay masjidka jaamica.

Sanadkii 35aad ee hijiriga waxaa ka dhacay [[dagaalkii ratiga]] ee u dhaxeeyay sayid [[Cali]] iyo [[Caa'isha binti Abiibakar|caaisha]]<ref>[http://www.islamicweb.com/goldenbook/camel.htm موقعة الجمل]، الكتاب [[شمس الدين الذهبي|الذهبي]]، [http://www.islamicweb.com الشبكة الإسلامية]. {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830180439/http://islamicweb.com/goldenbook/camel.htm|date=30 أغسطس 2017}}</ref>

Basra iyo [[kuufa]] waxaa kala maamuli jiray labo gudoomiye, [[Mucawiya|Mucaawiya]] ayaa [[ziyaad bin abiih]] isugu daray maamulkooda<ref> https://shamela.ws/book/12318/1143 </ref>, sanadkii 72H waxaa la dilay [[muscab bin zubeyr]] basra iyo ciraaq oo dhan gacanta umawiyiinta ayee gashay, sanadkii 75H waxaa lagu daray basra maamulkii [[xajaaj bin yuusuf]], sanadkii 82 hijrada waxaa ka bilaawday ciraaq kacdoon looga soo horjeedo xukunka umawiyiinta [[Ibni ashcas|ibnil ashcas]] ayaana hogaamiye ka ahaa, kacdoonkan ayaa ahaa mid khasaaro badan ka dhalatay waxa uuna socday ilaa 83H markaas oo lagu jabiyay [[ibni ashcas]] [[Dagaalkii deeru jamaajim|dagaalka deeru jamaajim]], 

Sanadkii 101H [[Yaziid bin muhalab]] ayaa qabsaday basra kacdoon ayuuna ku sameeyay umawiyiinta [[Yaziid bin cabdilmalik]] ayaa u diray ciidan xoogan oo [[Maslama bin cabdilmalik]] hogaaminaayo dagaal culus dhacay ka dib kacdoonka waa la soo afjaray [[Yaziid bin muhalab|Yaziid]] iyo ehelkiisana waa la xasuuqay.

